---
---
<section class="profile">
    <h2 class="section-title">PROFILE <small>// BIOGRAPHY</small></h2>
    <div class="grid-2">
        <div class="mil-border card">
            <h3>Interests</h3>
            <p>ゲーム研究、ストーリー考察、勉強会、ボーイスカウト</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mil-border card">
            <h3>Preferred Genres</h3>
            <p>TPS、RTS、シミュレーション</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mil-border card mt">
        <h3>Combat Training (Skills)</h3>
        <div class="skill-bar"><div class="fill" style="width: 85%">Unity / C#</div></div>
        <div class="skill-bar"><div class="fill orange" style="width: 25%">Unreal Engine</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mil-border card mt">
        <h3>Favorite Operations (Games)</h3>
        <p>Warframe、メタルギアシリーズ、ドールズフロントライン</p>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .section-title {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        border-left: 5px solid var(--accent-color);
        padding-left: 15px;
        color: var(--accent-color);
    }

    .section-title small {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .grid-2 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 20px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .grid-2 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }

    .card h3 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        color: var(--accent-color);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent-color-rgb), 0.2);
        padding-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .mt { margin-top: 20px; }

    .skill-bar {
        height: 12px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        position: relative;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .skill-bar .fill {
        height: 100%;
        background: var(--accent-color);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        padding-left: 10px;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: bold;
        white-space: nowrap;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(var(--accent-color-rgb), 0.3);
    }

    .skill-bar .fill.orange {
        background: var(--warning-color);
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(var(--accent-color-rgb), 0.2);
    }
</style>
